A4 inhibitors.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/73414/', '', 'Dirithromycin, Lincomycin, Clindamycin, Minocycline, Clindamycin, Vitamin A, Isotretinoin, Dexamethasone, Fluorometholone, Tretinoin, Methylprednisolone, More', 'Lesinurad, Febuxostat, Pegloticase, Sulfinpyrazone, Rasburicase, Probenecid', 1767369485);
