0 3A4 inhibitors.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/73442/', '', 'Lesinurad, Febuxostat, Pegloticase, Rasburicase, Probenecid, Allopurinol', '', 1767369485);
