A4 inhibitors.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/73487/', '', 'Caspofungin, Micafungin, Amphotericin B, Oteseconazole, Flucytosine, Anidulafungin', 'Lesinurad, Febuxostat, Pegloticase, Sulfinpyrazone, Rasburicase, Probenecid', 1767369485);
